rows.label: bf11320100_0012

Even without his arms, he may cause
you more trouble, one day.

rows.label: bf11320100_0020
rows.name: I didn't want to end it here...

rows.label: bf11320100_0030
rows.name:
He might deserve it, but...
He did...take care of my mother, so.

rows.label: bf11320100_0060
rows.name:
I suppose I can bring myself to step
foot on this flagship after all...
